{"tid":788590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾unwire又偷人文","createTime":"2018-08-21T14:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T14:59:33.000Z","uid":61560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"391d6d20134c393ddca1383d0fcbc2ee19c09951","tid":788590,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"unwire一向都垃圾<br />\n但今次對方出埋聲都扮睇唔到<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1981482401908363&amp;id=192678424122112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1981482401908363%26id%3D192678424122112&d=U1xicUYQoSLXF4XIAwMW3S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=9db445ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1981482401908363&amp;id=192678424122112</a><br />\n<br />\n又飛啦! Flyagain.la        55分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n#嚴正聲明<br />\n<br />\n小弟尋晚寫到零晨一點先出嘅「#估你唔到的北韓第二章：SIM Card篇」，今日立即被 <a href=\"http://UNWIRE.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUNWIRE.HK&d=U1xicUYQoSLXF4XIAwMW3S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ef101b67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UNWIRE.HK</a> 喺冇事先向我哋拎授權情況下偷文偷圖。<br />\n<br />\n兩道傳送門：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/08/21/unbelievablyexpensivekoryolinksimcard/life-tech/travel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2Funbelievablyexpensivekoryolinksimcard%2Flife-tech%2Ftravel%2F&d=U1xicUYQoSLXF4XIAwMW3S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0459d30b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/08/21/unbelievablyexpensivekoryolinksimcard/life-tech/travel/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/477164300494/posts/10161036957540495/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F477164300494%2Fposts%2F10161036957540495%2F&d=U1xicUYQoSLXF4XIAwMW3S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=9a884a0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/477164300494/posts/10161036957540495/</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/192678424122112/posts/1980055475384389/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F192678424122112%2Fposts%2F1980055475384389%2F&d=U1xicUYQoSLXF4XIAwMW3S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=db291401\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/192678424122112/posts/1980055475384389/</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋已經喺今日（21/8/2018）下午六時許留言要求Unwire 立即刪文停止侵權行為，可惜直到依家晚上九點左右對方並無行動。作為一間有咁上下歷史及規模網媒，實在可恥。<br />\n<br />\n我哋嚴正要求：<br />\n1. 立即刪除侵權文章及Facebook帖文<br />\n2. <a href=\"http://於Unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%96%BCUnwire.hk&d=U1xicUYQoSLXF4XIAwMW3S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a69e0195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">於Unwire.hk</a> Facebook Page發文公開向我哋道歉<br />\n3. 捐$100俾 雪橇國度 （要公開附上捐款收據）<br />\n<br />\n#花咗咁多錢為大家試用<br />\n#連唔該都冇就偷走哂<br />\n#你咁叻你唔去北韓做試用報告？<br />\n#尋晚捱眼訓都要寫埋先<br />\n#Unwire偷文偷圖可恥<br />\n#幫你推上各大傳媒好唔好？<br />\n#堅嬲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/224801_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F224801_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=c4ed60d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/224805_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F224805_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d2512ed1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d315656015ac8f775685b1fac67ce11d0ae767e1","tid":788590,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/21/225016_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F21%2F225016_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ef0598e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEPriceHK都有抄<br />\n但個fb page冇咩人睇<img src=\"/asset